description: In part 3, Lena truly begins to put her revenge plans into action when a friend gives her the number of a nefarious broker (notorious for under the table and sly deals). Everything is going smoothly until Lena’s friend slut-shames her during a ladies brunch causing her to dash off in a huff, but not before catching a glimpse of Giselle’s step-son (Lucas) and flirting up a storm. When Lena runs into Lucas at a party later that night, it’s the perfect combination of hormones and luck that send the two into a tizzy of sexual passion.
